This image displays the curated intellectual pedigree of the
community. To be shown in this graph, you must have submitted pedigree information to WormBase.
Individuals are placed on the graph according to the year they entered the community, determined as the year first published (including meeting abstracts) or from curated
lineage data, whichever is earliest. Individuals lacking pedigree or chronological information are excluded from the graph. You can update your data at
. Much of this data was curated by Cecilia Nakamura (cecilia@tazendra.caltech.edu).
Heuvel, Sander Jean Louis van den (1993-G)
